            Weekly Report
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.2rem; padding: 5px 0;">Period : From <<StartDate>> to <<EndDate>></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 1rem; padding: 5px 0;">AIS Manufacturing Pte Ltd.</td>
        <td style="width:130px; display: block; float: right;"></td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <td colspan="3">
            <table style="border: 1px solid #000; width: 100%; padding: 10px;">
